Description:
"Verify that upon cliking + button, modal box will open with the following details:
- Add Appointment (header)
- Doctor name (below header)
- Estimated Service Time (label and time)
- Patient (label)
- Username/mobile number (field)
- Nickname (field)
- Priority Patient (checkbox)
- Select date and time (drop down)
- ""By proceeding, I confirm that I have obtained consent to store the Patient Mobile no. & name."" (message)
- Cancel (button)
- Confirm (button)"

Suite/Test/Step Name: verifyElementVisible(findTestObject("Main/Page_PMRS Web Application/Dialog Elements/Labels, Titles/h1_Add Appointment"), STOP_ON_FAILURE)
verifyElementVisible(findTestObject("Main/Page_PMRS Web Application/Dialog Elements/Labels, Titles/p_DR DINA  TUTO"))
verifyElementVisible(findTestObject("Main/Page_PMRS Web Application/Dialog Elements/Labels, Titles/mat-label_SELECT DATE  TIME"), STOP_ON_FAILURE)
click(findTestObject("Main/Page_PMRS Web Application/Dialog Elements/Labels, Titles/input_SELECT DATE  TIME_mat-input-4"))

verifyElementText(findTestObject("Main/Page_PMRS Web Application/Dialog Elements/Labels, Titles/p_By proceeding I confirm that I have obtained consent to store the PATIENT MOBILE NO.  NAME."), "By proceeding, I confirm that I have obtained consent to store the PATIENT MOBILE NO. & NAME.")
